{"tid":1227111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[孫子兵法］敵不動我不動。所以敵不撤我不撤！","createTime":"2019-06-15T14:31:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T04:24:43.000Z","uid":184374,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"062cf7827ab2072015d3d057753b65178ee450c4","tid":1227111,"uid":184374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:31:49.000Z","msg":"話說我好鐘意睇書，最近就睇到孫子兵法。<br />\n孫子兵法有云：敵不動，我不動，敵欲動，我先動。<br />\n<br />\n意思即係敵人唔進攻，我地都唔進攻，敵人唔撤回，我地都唔撤退。敵人諗住之後捲土重來，我地要預先阻止呢個可能性。<br />\n<br />\n古人真係有好多大智慧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75b8d7333054c5210c8c8a584a6975b10ed4e093","tid":1227111,"uid":184374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:33:37.000Z","msg":"唔小心開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同打錯字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：敵人唔撤<del>回</del><span style=\"color: red;\">退</span>，我地都唔撤退。"},{"pid":"ec45630415e5b6236c7e9d22f33f3e4b64072233","tid":1227111,"uid":184374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:19:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7168c5f7cea6edc36c1ae00ff521a0f0c091cc9c","tid":1227111,"uid":184374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:51:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1625f3fa3dc254c3ca4c12838df2e9014b8e3085","tid":1227111,"uid":184374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T18:00:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8dc17b99cd9db042201a9fa4baed20896f8f6cdc","tid":1227111,"uid":184374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T01:18:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2ce837352afe4423240275cdf8cdbde28d0eea37","tid":1227111,"uid":184374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T04:24:43.000Z","msg":"推"}]}